cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about deep learning models for visual saliency prediction, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper specifically focuses on the choice of loss function in these models, which is a key aspect of training deep neural networks and falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces new loss functions, which could potentially fall under neural networks (cs.NE) or multimedia (cs.MM).
